[SkillPath "bidding_conventions/jacoby_2nt_splinters"]
[Student "S"]
{You have a perfect Jacoby 2NT raise. Partner's rebid is 3\H. What is your next bid? 

When partner shows an above average opener it is your duty to make a control bid if you can. So you bid 3\S. Partner now bids 4NT and it is your turn. 

This is Blackwood. You respond 5\H for two Aces and partner bids the slam.}

